    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos((wp.cos(tmp + 0.97) + v0))
    v1 = (tmp + (tmp * wp.cos(v2 + 0.91)))
    v2 = wp.exp(tmp)
    v1 = wp.exp(0.65)
    data[tid] = v0
